body:
We are doing #79584 to dogfood the experimental API. The change involved https://github.com/microsoft/vscode-css-languageservice/pull/174 and https://github.com/microsoft/vscode/pull/79962.

Once https://github.com/microsoft/vscode/issues/23927 is finalized and LSP library adopted it, we should remove the changes introduced in both PRs to do this cleanly through LSP.

@aeschli fyi

